    dc:description "FIGURE 179. Chelae of Gonatopus species holotypes. A: G. acuminatus (Olmi). B: G. cafer (Olmi). C: G. ceres (Olmi). D: G. fuscus (Olmi). Scale bar: A: 0.07 mm; B, C: 0.09 mm; D: 0.08 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3337034/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3337032>
    dc:description "FIGURE 178. Habitus of Gonatopus species: group 3. A: G. acuminatus (Olmi), ♀ holotype in dorsal view. B, C: G. mixtus Olmi, ♀ holotype in dorsal (B) and lateral (C) view. Scale bar: A: 2.31 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3337032/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3337048>
    dc:description "FIGURE 186. Habitus of Gonatopus species holotypes. A: G. pluvialis Olmi, ♀ in dorsal view. B, C: G. ruvidus Olmi, ♀ in dorsal (B) and lateral (C) view. D: G. bellicosus Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov.: ♀ in dorsal view; mesosoma sculpture. Scale bar: A: 3.00 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3337048/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3337036>
    dc:description "FIGURE 180. Gonatopus: group 3. A: G. acuminatus (Olmi), mesosoma of ♀ holotype in lateral view. B: G. ceres (Olmi), ♀ from Namibia, Kuiseb River: mesoscutum + mesoscutellum + metapectal-propodeal disc + propodeal declivity in dorsal view. C, D, I: G. fuscus (Olmi), ♀ holotype: head in frontal view (C); mesosoma in lateral view (D); habitus in dorsal view (I). E, F: G. hantamensis Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov., ♀ holotype: mesoscutum + mesoscutellum + metapectal-propodeal disc + propodeal declivity in dorsal view (E); mesosoma in lateral view (F). G: G. madecassus Olmi, ♀ holotype: mesoscutum + mesoscutellum + metapectal-propodeal disc + propodeal declivity in dorsal view. H: G. nicator Olmi, ♀ holotype: mesosoma in lateral view. Scale bar: A: 1.18 mm; B: 0.85 mm; C: 0.29 mm; D, F: 1.23 mm; E: 0.82 mm; G: 1.24 mm; H: 1.46 mm; I: 1.13 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3337036/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3337042>
    dc:description "FIGURE 183. Gonatopus: group 3. A, B, G: G. robertsoni Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov.: mesoscutum + mesoscutellum + metapectal-propodeal disc + propodeal declivity in dorsal view (A) and mesosoma in lateral view (B) of ♀ holotype; chela of paratype from South Africa, 33°44.090’S 21°55.654’E (G). C, D: G. scholtzi Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov., ♀ holotype: mesoscutum + mesoscutellum + metapectal-propodeal disc + propodeal declivity in dorsal view (C) and mesosoma in lateral view (D). E, F: G. schwarzorum Guglielmino & Olmi, ♀ holotype: mesosoma in dorsal (E) and lateral (F) view. H: chela of G. ruber (Olmi), holotype. Scale bar: A, C: 0.60 mm; B: 0.90 mm; D: 0.93 mm; E, F: 1.00 mm; G: 0.07 mm; H: 0.08 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3337042/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3337050>
    dc:description "FIGURE 187. Chelae of Gonatopus species holotypes.A: G. ruvidus Olmi. B: G. scholtzi Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov. C: G. schwarzorum Guglielmino & Olmi Scale bar: A: 0.14 mm; B: 0.05 mm; C: 0.07 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3337050/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3337040>
    dc:description "FIGURE 182.Chelae of Gonatopus species holotypes.A: G. hantamensis Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov. B: G. madecassus Olmi. C: G. mixtus Olmi. D: G. nicator Olmi. E: G. pluvialis Olmi. F: G. robertsoni Olmi, Copeland & van Noort sp. nov. Scale bar: A, D, F: 0.09 mm; B: 0.13 mm; C, E: 0.07 mm." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3337040/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

